name: Abandoned Fun
description:
At one time, people played basketball here. The atmosphere was filled with trash talk and competition, laughter and fun...
No one even walks by here anymore, no one except me with my camera in hand.

Black and White Film Photography 

Gear i used 
Camera: Nikon FM10 
Lens: 35-70mm f3.5-4.8
Film: Ilford HP5+
